---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About — TripLion"
  description="TripLion is a travel planning app built to keep itineraries, maps, routes, stays, and trip to-dos in one calm place."
  path="/about"
>
  <main class="narrow-page">
    <h1>Travel planning should not take more work than the trip.</h1>
    <p>TripLion started from a simple frustration: every trip meant a spreadsheet, a dozen browser tabs, a map on one screen and a to-do list on another. We wanted one place that held all of it, without the clutter.</p>
    <p>So we are building a planner where your itinerary and your map live in the same view, where checklists build themselves from what you have already planned, and where planning with other people feels as easy as texting them.</p>
    <p>We are a small team, and we are building this in the open during early access, which means the people who join now shape what it becomes.</p>
    <div class="soft-cta">
      <p>Want in early?</p>
      <a href="/#waitlist" class="pill-button">Join the waitlist</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
